Package: deformetricar
Type: Package
Title: R Client for the Deformetrica Shape Registration Toolkit
Version: 0.2.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Alexander", "Bates", email = "alexander.shakeel.bates@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Gregory", "Jefferis", role = "aut"))
Description: Wraps the Deformetrica (>= 4.3) command-line tools so that 3D
    coordinates and neuron objects can be transformed by fitted diffeomorphisms
    via geodesic shooting and flow. Reads and writes VTK object formats and
    provides sensible defaults for registering fly connectome neurons.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
URL: https://github.com/alexanderbates/deformetricar
BugReports: https://github.com/alexanderbates/deformetricar/issues
Depends: R (>= 4.1)
Imports: nat, Morpho, Rvcg, xml2, catmaid, rgl, nat.nblast
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    withr,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    nat.flybrains,
    insectbrainr,
    gifski
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
